# Importing Raven bitmap b4 the shaders (lower quality to save some resources but it shouldn't be noticeable)

# RAVEN 1
GenerateBitmap objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_cc workingdir\bitmaps\ODST\Raven1\odst_raven_1_cc.dds
GenerateBitmap objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_diff workingdir\bitmaps\ODST\Raven1\odst_raven_1_diff.dds
GenerateBitmap objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_illum workingdir\bitmaps\ODST\Raven1\odst_raven_1_illum.dds
ForEach bitm named: objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_diff GenerateMipmaps
ForEach bitm named: objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_illum GenerateMipmaps

CreateTag bitm objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_zbump
ForEach bitm named: objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_zbump ImportBitmap 0 workingdir\bitmaps\ODST\Raven1\odst_raven_1_zbump.dds linear
ForEach bitm named: objects\characters\masterchief\bitmaps\odst_raven_1_zbump GenerateMipmaps

