PortTag objects\characters\masterchief\shaders\spartan_shoulder_s9_spi.shader
PortTag objects\characters\masterchief\shaders\spartan_leg_s9_spi.shader
Exit

# Shader Adjustment
ForEach shader startingwith: objects\characters\masterchief\shaders\odst_raven SetArgument diffuse_coefficient 2